fr.B4D.dofus.items

Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.B4D.dofus.items.Item
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CeremonialItem, Consumable, Equipment, Harness, Idol, ItemInterface, Monster, Mount, Pet, Resource, Set, Sidekick, Weapon

    public class Item
extends Object
implements Monster, Weapon, Equipment, Set, Pet, Mount, Consumable, Resource, CeremonialItem, Sidekick, Idol, Harness
    The Item class represent an item in the game.

    An item is represented by a url, an id, a name, an image url and a type.
